{"name": "boardlib", "metadata": {"name": "boardlib", "version": "0.9.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["bs4", "pandas", "requests"], "summary": "Utilities for interacting with climbing board APIs", "upload_time": 1732219299}, "documentation": ["# BoardLib \ud83e\uddd7\u200d\u2640\ufe0f\n\nUtilities for interacting with (undocumented) climbing board APIs.\n\n## Installation \ud83e\uddba\n\n`python3 -m pip install boardlib`\n\n## Usage \u2328\ufe0f\n\n### Databases \ud83d\udcbe\n\nTo download the climb database for a given board:\n\n`boardlib database <board_name> <database_path>`\n\nThis command will first download a [sqlite](https://www.sqlite.org/index.html) database file to the given path. After downloading, the database will then use the undocumented sync API to synchronize it with the latest available data. The database contains only the publicly available data. User data is not synchronized. If a database already exists as `database_path`, the command will skip the download step and only perform the synchronization.\n\nNOTE: The Moonboard is not currently supported for the database command. Contributions are welcome.\n\n#### Supported Boards \ud83d\udef9\n\nAll [Aurora Climbing](https://auroraclimbing.com/) based boards (Kilter, Tension, etc.).\n\n### Logbooks \ud83d\udcda\n\nTo download your logbook entries for a given board:\n\n`boardlib logbook <board_name> --username=<username> --output=<output_file_name>.csv --grade-type=\"hueco\" --database=<local_database_file>`\n\nThis outputs a CSV file with the following fields:\n\n```json\n[\"board\", \"angle\", \"climb_name\", \"date\", \"logged_grade\", \"displayed_grade\", \"difficulty\", \"is_benchmark\", \"tries\", \"is_mirror\", \"sessions_count\", \"tries_total\", \"is_repeat\", \"is_ascent\", \"comment\"]\n```\n\nFor example, the command\n\n`boardlib tension --username=\"Luke EF\" --output=\"tension.csv\" --grade-type=\"hueco\" --database=\"tension.db\"`\n\nwould output a file named `tension.csv` with the following contents:\n\n```\nboard,angle,climb_name,date,logged_grade,displayed_grade,difficulty,is_benchmark,tries,is_mirror,sessions_count,tries_total,is_repeat,is_ascent,comment\ntension,40,trash bag better,2024-06-17 16:21:23,V3,V3,16.0,False,3,False,1,3,False,True,\ntension,40,Bumble,2024-06-17 16:28:23,V3,V3,16.0,True,1,True,1,1,False,True,\ntension,40,sender2,2024-06-17 16:38:06,V5,V5,20.0,False,2,False,1,2,False,True,\n...\n```\nWhen no local database is provided, displayed_grade and difficulty remain empty.\nSee `boardlib --help` for a full list of supported board names and feature flags.\n\n#### Supported Boards \ud83d\udef9\n\nCurrently all [Aurora Climbing](https://auroraclimbing.com/) based boards (Kilter, Tension, etc.) and all variations of the [Moonboard](https://moonboard.com/) should be supported.\n\n## Bugs \ud83d\udc1e and Feature Requests \ud83d\uddd2\ufe0f\n\nPlease create an issue in the [issue tracker](https://github.com/lemeryfertitta/BoardLib/issues) to report bugs or request additional features. Contributions are welcome and appreciated.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "boardlib", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "boardlib.util.grades", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "boardlib.util.grades.FONT_TO_HUECO", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "boardlib.util", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "boardlib.api.moon.get_session", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "username", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "password", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.logbook_pages", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "session", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "page_size", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "page", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.raw_logbook_entries_for_page", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "session", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "entry_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "page_size", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "page", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.raw_logbook_entries", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "session", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "logbook_page_size", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "entry_page_size", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.get_my_ranking", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "session", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "angle", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.get_summary_by_benchmark_tries", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "session", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "angle", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.logbook_entries", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "username", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "password", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "grade_type", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.get_map_markers", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "session", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["> ```\n> return\n>\n> list of board objects. For example:\n> {\n>\n> source:3: (ERROR/3) Unexpected indentation.\n>\n> \"Name\": \"The School Room\",\n> \"Description\": \"The original MoonBoard in the legendary School Room.\n> ```\n\nThe School Room, Sheffield is a high spec members-only training facility for intermediate to advanced climbers aged 18+ who wish to improve their strength and endurance for climbing.\n\nOpen 24/7, 7-days a week.\",\n\n: > \"Image\": \"/Content/Account/Users/MoonBoards/SchoolRoom.jpg\",\n  > \"Latitude\": 53.386304,\n  > \"Longitude\": -1.47619,\n  > \"IsCommercial\": true,\n  > \"IsLed\": true,\n  > \"LatLng\": \\[53.386304, -1.47619\\]\n\n  }\n"]}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.gym_boards", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "session", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "boardlib.api.moon.HOST", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.BOARD_IDS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.ANGLES_TO_IDS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.ATTEMPTS_TO_COUNT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.moon.IDS_TO_ANGLES", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "boardlib.db", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "boardlib.db.aurora", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "boardlib.db.aurora.download_database", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "output_file", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["The sqlite3 database is stored in the assets folder of the APK files for the Android app of each board.\n\nThis function downloads the latest APK file for the board's Android app and extracts the database from it.\n\\:param board: The board to download the database for.\n\\:param output_file: The file to write the database to.\n"]}, {"name": "boardlib.db.aurora.sync_shared_tables", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "database", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Syncs the public tables from the remote database to the local database.\nIf the last sync is too old, it is possible that the remote will respond with an empty object.\nThere appears to be some limit to the amount of data that can be transferred via a sync, but this limit is opaque.\n\n```\nparam board\n\nThe board to sync the database for.\n\nparam database\n\nThe sqlite3 database file to sync.\n\nreturns\n\na mapping of synchronized table names to counts of inserted/updated/deleted rows.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "boardlib.db.aurora.insert_rows_default", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "connection", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "table_name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "rows", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.db.aurora.insert_rows_climb_stats", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "connection", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "table_name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "rows", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "boardlib.db.aurora.APP_PACKAGE_NAMES", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.db.aurora.ROW_INSERTERS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "boardlib.__main__", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "boardlib.__main__.logbook_entries", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "username", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "password", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "grade_type", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "database", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.__main__.write_entries", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "output_file", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "entries", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "no_headers", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "fields", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.__main__.handle_database_command", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.__main__.handle_logbook_command", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.__main__.add_database_parser", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "subparsers", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.__main__.add_logbook_parser", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "subparsers", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.__main__.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "boardlib.__main__.LOGBOOK_FIELDS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.login", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "username", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "password", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.explore", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.get_logbook", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "user_id", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.get_grades", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.get_gyms", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": [":return:\n    {\n        \"gyms\": [\n            {\n                'id': 373656,\n                'username': '<username>',\n                'name': '<name>',\n                'latitude': 48.10135,\n                'longitude': 11.30113\n            },\n            ...\n        ]\n    }"]}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.get_user", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "user_id", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.get_climb_stats", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "climb_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "angle", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.get_climb_name", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "climb_id", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.get_climb_name_from_db", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "database", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "climb_uuid", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Add a function to get climb name from local database"]}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.user_sync", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "user_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "tables", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "walls", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "wall_expungements", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "shared_syncs", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "user_syncs", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["---\nparam tables: |-\n  list of tables to download. The following are valid:\n  \"products\",\n  \"product_sizes\",\n  \"holes\",\n  \"leds\",\n  \"products_angles\",\n  \"layouts\",\n  \"product_sizes_layouts_sets\",\n  \"placements\",\n  \"sets\",\n  \"placement_roles\",\n  \"climbs\",\n  \"climb_stats\",\n  \"beta_links\",\n  \"attempts\",\n  \"kits\",\n  \"users\",\n  \"walls\",\n  \"wall_expungements\",\n  \"draft_climbs\",\n  \"ascents\",\n  \"bids\",\n  \"tags\",\n  \"circuits\",\nparam wall_expungements: list of walls to delete\nparam walls: list of walls to upload\nparm shared_syncs: |-\n  list of {\"table_name\": \\<table_name>, \"last_synchronized_at\": \\<last_synchronized_at>}\n  e.g. \\[{'table_name': 'climbs', 'last_synchronized_at': '2023-06-07 20:36:41.578003'}\\]\n  It looks like the largest table (climbs) won't synchronize unless it has a shared_sync with last_synchronized_at set.\n---\n"]}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.shared_sync", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "tables", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "shared_syncs", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Shared syncs are used to download data from the board. They are not authenticated.\n\n```\nparam tables\n\nlist of tables to download. The following are valid:\n\"products\",\n\"product_sizes\",\n\"holes\",\n\"leds\",\n\"products_angles\",\n\"layouts\",\n\"product_sizes_layouts_sets\",\n\"placements\",\n\"sets\",\n\"placement_roles\",\n\"climbs\",\n\"climb_stats\",\n\"beta_links\",\n\"attempts\",\n\"kits\",\n```\n"]}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.gym_boards", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.download_image", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "image_filename", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "output_filename", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.generate_uuid", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.save_ascent", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "user_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "climb_uuid", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "angle", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "is_mirror", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "attempt_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "bid_count", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "quality", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "difficulty", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "is_benchmark", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "comment", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "climbed_at", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "boardlib.api.aurora.save_attempt", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "board", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "token", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "user_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "climb_uuid", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "angle", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "is_mirror", "type": null, "default": null}, {